thread.title: Junior Eurovision

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Junior Eurovision
text: Brand new series kicks off tonight where we commence the search for the act that will represent Ireland and compete in the Junior Eurovision song contest. Yes, there is a JUNIOR Eurovision folks, and this will be Ireland's first time competing in it. Eoghan McDemott is on presenting duty while Eurovision winner Niamh Kavanagh, singer-songwriter Brian Kennedy and Seo Linn's Stiofan O Fearail make up the judging panel.
